# Active Directory Home Lab Project

This project is the start of my personal IT home lab, where I’m gaining hands-on experience with **Windows Server 2022** and **Active Directory**.  

The goal is to build a small virtual network using **Oracle VirtualBox** to simulate a real-world business environment.  

### Table of Contents
- [Tools & Environment](#tools--environment)  
- [Objectives](#objectives)  
