## Step 4: Network Configuration and Domain Connection

Configured network settings and connected the Windows 11 client to the domain:  
- Static IPs: Server `10.1.10.2`, Client `10.1.10.3`  
- Joined client to **MelTech.com** domain  
- Verified connection in Active Directory (Desktop01 appeared under Computers)  
- Enabled Remote Desktop access and connected using server IP  

