## Step 5: User Account Management and Security Policies

Managed user accounts and applied security policies:  
- Reset, activate, disable, and delete accounts  
- Login hour restrictions: Thomas C Anderson Mon–Fri, 6 a.m.–6 p.m.  
- Group Policy changes:  
  - Maximum password age: 90 days  
  - Account lockout threshold: 3 failed attempts  
  - Lockout duration: 360 minutes  
- Verified policies with failed login attempts  
- Unlocked account afterward  

